r friends here that have small businesses. Now, we\'re out of our mother\'s garage still harnessing the vigor of the Rochestarian small business owners and partnering with them to increase value and creating win-win situations by expanding their online presence.</span></h4>\";s:20:\"text_selected_editor\";s:7:\"tinymce\";s:5:\"autop\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"5978e96c3f228\";s:19:\"_sow_form_timestamp\";s:13:\"1502826076075\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:1;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:1;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"6e9ff68b-622d-49f5-b8c9-fcaa17766e19\";s:5:\"style\";a:4:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";s:17:\"content_alignment\";s:4:\"left\";s:11:\"title_color\";s:7:\"#443f3f\";s:14:\"headings_color\";s:7:\"#443f3f\";}}}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"visual\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:108:\"<p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p>\";s:6:\"filter\";s:1:\"1\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:30:\"WP_Widget_Black_Studio_TinyMCE\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:2;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:2;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"99703642-9540-4a90-b3a8-7ef00bb7694a\";s:5:\"style\";a:4:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";s:17:\"content_alignment\";s:4:\"left\";s:11:\"title_color\";s:7:\"#443f3f\";s:14:\"headings_color\";s:7:\"#443f3f\";}}}i:3;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:39:\"Our Process: The Secret to Your Success\";s:4:\"text\";s:2240:\"<h5>Here is one way to think about what we actually do...</h5>\n<h5>Imagine your new creation, the Frankenstein Cyborg Baby is finally ready and you are so excited.  You just know that they are gonna be the newest and coolest, and totally replace the boring robot butlers forever.  But you are stuck selling them to your friends or passerbys which doesn\'t work well and brings you away from the fun part.  And who would blame you!?  You don\'t have time for that boring stuff when you are busy coming up with a better design for the baby\'s fully reticulating neck and programming it to collect cobwebs off the ceiling.</h5>\n<h5>That\'s where we come in!  So I build you a fancy gallery to sell your Frankenstein Babies, making your operation look top notch. We can call that \"d<strong>evelopment\".</strong></h5>\n<h5>We talk some more and while you like the store you would like it more if people were actually going into it....</h5>\n<h5>So here is where it gets interesting.  I plan an event at The Festival which will demonstrate your Creation\'s cool abilities and I paint a sign saying ‘The Creation Demonstration coming to The Festival, Friday’, that’s \"<strong>advertising\"</strong>.</h5>\n<h5>If you make an army of Scaled Down Abominable Creations and we walk them into town as they carry that sign, that’s \"<strong>promotion\"</strong>.</h5>\n<h5>If the army gets hacked, starts taking over the world, and The Daily Show writes a story about it, that’s \"<strong>publicity\"</strong>.</h5>\n<h5>And if I get the world to then laugh about it, that’s<strong> \"public relations\"</strong>.</h5>\n<h5>If the town’s citizens go to see your creation, I show them the many ways it can entertain and make them happier, explain how much fun they’ll have spending money on one, answer their questions and ultimately, they buy a lot at the event, that’s \"<strong>sales\"</strong>.</h5>\n<h5>And if I planned this entire thing, that’s \"<strong>marketing\".</strong></h5>\n<h5> </h5>\n<h5><strong>This is the secret to your success</strong> and what we do in a nutshell!!  The only difference is the majority of it can be efficiently done online now, so thats why we will call it <strong>WEB development and marketing.</strong></h5>\";s:20:\"text_selected_editor\";s:7:\"tinymce\";s:5:\"autop\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"599288ae826c2\";s:19:\"_sow_form_timestamp\";s:13:\"1502826900484\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\"