freelancers who seized the opportunity to use our talents to help out our friends here with small businesses. From this beginning we’ve harnessed the vigor of the Rochestarian small business owner and banded with them to increase value and produce better brands by expanding their online presence.</span></h3>\";s:20:\"text_selected_editor\";s:7:\"tinymce\";s:5:\"autop\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"5978e96c3f228\";s:19:\"_sow_form_timestamp\";s:13:\"1502775401848\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:6:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\";s:4:\"grid\";i:1;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:1;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"6e9ff68b-622d-49f5-b8c9-fcaa17766e19\";s:5:\"style\";a:5:{s:27:\"background_image_attachment\";b:0;s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";s:17:\"content_alignment\";s:4:\"left\";s:11:\"title_color\";s:7:\"#443f3f\";s:14:\"headings_color\";s:7:\"#443f3f\";}}}i:2;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:11:\"Our Process\";s:4:\"text\";s:1802:\"<h4>That\'s where I come in.... so I build you a fancy store to sell them in making it all look very professional. Well call that <strong>development.</strong></h4>\n<h4>We talk some more and while you like the store you would like it more if people were actually going into it....</h4>\n<h4>So here is where it gets interesting.  I plan an event at The Festival which will demonstrate your Creation\'s cool abilities and I paint a sign saying ‘The Creation Demonstration coming to The Festival, Friday’, that’s <strong>advertising</strong>.</h4>\n<h4>If you make an army of Scaled Down Abominable Creations and we walk them into town as they carry that sign, that’s <strong>promotion</strong>.</h4>\n<h4>If the army gets hacked, starts taking over the world, and The Daily Show writes a story about it, that’s <strong>publicity</strong>.</h4>\n<h4>And if I get the world to then laugh about it, that’s<strong> public relations</strong>.</h4>\n<h4>If the town’s citizens go to see your creation, I show them the many ways it can entertain and mak