ign: center;\"><span style=\"color: #999999;\">Flower City Online is  THE  Web Operations and Marketing Agency in Rochester. We are all born and bred here in Rochester giving us the opportunity to start networking for our customers way before we even knew them. We\'re a rag tag group of maverick freelancers who seized the opportunity to use our talents to help out our friends here that have small businesses. Now, we\'re out of our mother\'s garage still harnessing the vigor of the Rochestarian small business owners and partnering with them to increase value and creating win-win situations by expanding their online presence.</span></h4>\";s:20:\"text_selected_editor\";s:7:\"tinymce\";s:5:\"autop\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"5978e96c3f228\";s:19:\"_sow_form_timestamp\";s:13:\"1502826076075\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:6:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\";s:4:\"grid\";i:1;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:1;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"6e9ff68b-622d-49f5-b8c9-fcaa17766e19\";s:5:\"style\";a:5:{s:27:\"background_image_attachment\";b:0;s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";s:17:\"content_alignment\";s:4:\"left\";s:11:\"title_color\";s:7:\"#443f3f\";s:14:\"headings_color\";s:7:\"#443f3f\";}}}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"visual\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:108:\"<p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p>\";s:6:\"filter\";s:1:\"1\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:30:\"WP_Widget_Black_Studio_TinyMCE\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:2;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:2;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"99703642-9540-4a90-b3a8-7ef00bb7694a\";s:5:\"style\";a:4:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";s:17:\"content_alignment\";s:4:\"left\";s:11:\"title_color\";s:7:\"#443f3f\";s:14:\"headings_color\";s:7:\"#443f3f\";}}}i:3;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:11:\"Our Process\";s:4:\"text\";s:2977:\"<h5>When you send in your Expansion Idea it gets uploaded to a flash drive in Tibet where a monastery full of the most spiritual monks meditate to check basic viability of that idea in this market.  Chakras are performed.  Auras can flare. And if the idea marinades in Earth\'s ether just right and with enough energy to compel a white dove to soar from Tibet to New York whilst carrying that flash drive, then the idea was meant to be.  Suggested tweaks or additions will come in the form of intuition which we will communicate to you upon visiting for tea. Namaste.</h5>\n<h5>But enough about the initial process. What happens after that?</h5>\n<h5>Well, here is one way to think about it:</h5>\n<h5>Imagine your new Frankenstein Cyborg Baby <strong>creation</strong> is ready and you are so excited.  You just know that they are gonna be the newest and coolest, and totally replace robot butlers forever.  But you are stuck selling them to a few people out of your garage which doesn\'t work well and brings you away from the fun part, like coming up with a better design for its fully reticulating neck and programming it to collect cobwebs off the ceiling.</h5>\n<h5>That\'s where we come in!  So I build you a fancy store to sell your Frankenstein Babies, making your operation look very professional. Well call that <strong>development.</strong></h5>\n<h5>We talk some more and while you like the store you would like it more if people were actually going into it....</h5>\n<h5>So here is where it gets interesting.  I plan an event at The Festival which will demonstrate your Creation\'s cool abilities and I paint a sign saying ‘The Creation Demonstration coming to The Festival, Friday’, that’s <strong>advertising</strong>.</h5>\n<h5>If you make an army of Scaled Down Abominable Creations and we walk them into town as they carry that sign, that’s <strong>promotion</strong>.</h5>\n<h5>If the army gets hacked, starts taking over the world, and The Daily Show writes a story about it, that’s <strong>publicity</strong>.</h5>\n<h5>And if I get the world to then laugh about it, that’s<strong> public relations</strong>.</h5>\n<h5>If the town’s citizens go to see your creation, I show them the many ways it can entertain and make them happier, explain how much fun they’ll have spending money on one, answer their questions and ultimately, they buy a lot at the event, that’s <strong>sales</strong>.</h5>\n<h5>And if I planned this entire thing, that’s <strong>marketing.</strong></h5>\n<h5> </h5>\n<h5><strong>This is the secret to your success</strong> and what we do in a nutshell!!  The only difference is we do this all online, so it is called <strong>WEB development and marketing.</strong></h5>\n<h5>So there is the secret!</h5>\n<h5>Also, the universe is telling me that by getting our <strong>monthly newsletter</strong> you will become fully enlightened and reach nirvana... as long as by \"nirvana\" you mean \"business goals\". Namaste.</h5>\";s:20:\"text_selected_editor\";s:7:\"tinymce\";s:5:\"autop\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"599288ae826c2\";s:19:\"_sow_form_timestamp\";s:13:\"1502777703206\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:3;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:3;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"668deca7-bdb1-456c-9df0-a8c81e618521\";s:5:\"style\";a:4:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";s:17:\"content_alignment\";s:4:\"left\";s:11:\"title_color\";s:7:\"#443f3f\";s:14:\"headings_color\";s:7:\"#443f3f\";}}}}s:5:\"grids\";a:4:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:\"cells\";i:1;s:5:\"style\";a:7:{s:6:\"gutter\";s:3:\"0px\";s:11:\"row_stretch\";s:14:\"full-stretched\";s:14:\"cell_alignment\";s:10:\"flex-start\";s:5:\"align\";s:0:\"\";s:16:\"background_image\";s:3:\"752\";s:7:\"overlay\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"overlay_color\";s:7:\"#000000\";}}i:1;a:2:{s:5:\"cells\";i:1;s:5:\"style\";a:5:{s:11:\"row_stretch\";s:4:\"full\";s:14:\"cell_alignment\";s:10:\"flex-start\";s:5:\"align\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"overlay\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"overlay_color\";s:7:\"#000000\";}}i:2;a:2:{s:5:\"cells\";i:1;s:5:\"style\";a:6:{s:11:\"row_stretch\";s:14:\"full