ng> \"public relations\"</strong>.</h5>\n<h5>If the town’s citizens go to see your creation, I show them the many ways it can entertain and make them happier, explain how much fun they’ll have spending money on one, answer their questions and ultimately, they buy a lot at the event, that’s \"<strong>sales\"</strong>.</h5>\n<h5>And if I planned this entire thing, that’s \"<strong>marketing\".</strong></h5>\n<h5> </h5>\n<h5><strong>This is the secret to your success</strong> and what we do in a nutshell!!  The only difference is the majority of it can be efficiently done online now, so thats why we will call it <strong>WEB development and marketing.</strong></h5>\";s:20:\"text_selected_editor\";s:7:\"tinymce\";s:5:\"autop\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"599288ae826c2\";s:19:\"_sow_form_timestamp\";s:13:\"1502826900484\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:6:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\";s:4:\"grid\";i:3;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:3;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"668deca7-bdb1-456c-9df0-a8c81e618521\";s:5:\"style\";a:5:{s:27:\"background_image_attachment\";b:0;s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";s:17:\"content_alignment\";s:4:\"left\";s:11:\"title_color\";s:7:\"#443f3f\";s:14:\"headings_color\";s:7:\"#443f3f\";}}}}s:5:\"grids\";a:4:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:\"cells\";i:1;s:5:\"style\";a:7:{s:6:\"gutter\";s:3:\"0px\";s:11:\"row_stretch\";s:14:\"full-stretched\";s:14:\"cell_alignment\";s:10:\"flex-start\";s:5:\"align\";s:0:\"\";s:16:\"background_image\";s:3:\"752\";s:7:\"overlay\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"overlay_color\";s:7:\"#000000\";}}i:1;a:2:{s:5:\"cells\";i:1;s:5:\"style\";a:5:{s:11:\"row_stretch\";s:4:\"full\";s:14:\"cell_alignment\";s:10:\"flex-start\";s:5:\"align\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"overlay\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"overlay_color\";s:7:\"#000000\";}}i:2;a:2:{s:5:\"cells\";i:1;s:5:\"style\";a:6:{s:11:\"row_stretch\";s:14:\"full-stretched\";s:14:\"cell_alignment\";s:10:\"flex-start\";s:5:\"align\";s:0:\"\";s:16:\"background_image\";s:3:\"882\";s:7:\"overlay\";b:1;s:13:\"overlay